1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 12=

19
00:01:19,250 --> 00:01:21,220
Zuixian House's ledgers.

20
00:01:21,610 --> 00:01:22,810
(11th Month, 12th Month, 1st Month)
I had someone acquire them.

21
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,829
Such refined wording.

22
00:01:24,830 --> 00:01:27,450
You stole them.

23
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:34,500
Do you see anything?

24
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:36,900
For a place this busy,

25
00:01:37,660 --> 00:01:40,010
the reported daily takings
are surprisingly low.

26
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:45,240
(Bureau of Commerce and Industry)

27
00:01:45,690 --> 00:01:47,420
Bureau of Commerce and Industry?

28
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:49,810
I established a new office.

29
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:50,980
Bei,

30
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,290
have

31
00:01:52,460 --> 00:01:53,860
Xiao Ling and Hulv

32
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:55,170
inspect Zuixian House.

33
00:02:06,490 --> 00:02:07,900
What's going on?

34
00:02:08,020 --> 00:02:08,850
Why such a mess?

35
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:13,300
Your Highnesses,

36
00:02:13,530 --> 00:02:14,809
the second floor is under repair.

37
00:02:14,810 --> 00:02:16,739
I wouldn't want your clothes soiled.

38
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:18,769
Weren't you open just two days ago?

39
00:02:18,770 --> 00:02:20,500
Why start repairs the moment we arrive?

40
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,769
You've misunderstood.

41
00:02:21,770 --> 00:02:22,899
The roof has been leaking.

42
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:24,179
We've been repairing it for days.

43
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,769
If you come back tomorrow,

44
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:27,020
it'll be finished.

45
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:27,970
Open the door.

46
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,220
Your Highness,

47
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,370
do you truly wish to see it?

48
00:02:31,610 --> 00:02:33,020
You won't let us in?

49
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:34,850
What are you hiding?

50
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:44,090
What's that smell?

51
00:02:44,210 --> 00:02:45,250
Close it.

52
00:02:48,370 --> 00:02:49,979
We just painted.

53
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:51,259
The smell is rather strong.

54
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:53,340
I'm running an honest business.

55
00:02:53,420 --> 00:02:54,580
Your Highnesses,

56
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,180
what exactly are you investigating?

57
00:02:58,370 --> 00:03:00,209
The Bureau of Commerce and Industry

58
00:03:00,210 --> 00:03:02,970
investigates everything.

59
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:07,250
Your Highness,

60
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,370
nothing suspicious.

61
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,840
They start renovating
the moment we inspect them.

62
00:03:19,050 --> 00:03:20,300
Who would believe that?

63
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:24,060
Only senior court officials
knew about this inspection.

64
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,090
Yet Zuixian House
got wind of it beforehand.

65
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:27,690
That means someone at court

66
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,739
is in league with them.

67
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:31,529
If they knew in advance,

68
00:03:31,530 --> 00:03:32,769
could that paint

69
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:34,850
have been used to cover another smell?

70
00:03:38,810 --> 00:03:40,410
Should we inspect them again?

71
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:42,459
We can't inspect them openly now.

72
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:43,580
We'll have to go undercover.

73
00:03:46,490 --> 00:03:49,250
I heard Zuixian House is hiring dancers.

74
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:50,220
Why don't

75
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,850
I audition

76
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:53,900
and look into it while I'm there?

77
00:03:54,050 --> 00:03:55,240
No.

78
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,609
The Princess Special is all the rage.
Everyone knows you.

79
00:03:57,610 --> 00:03:59,340
Besides, we just inspected Zuixian House.

80
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:00,780
True.

81
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:04,250
I think

82
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,690
Her Highness has a point.

83
00:04:05,810 --> 00:04:06,979
We simply need

84
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:07,929
someone

85
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:08,850
they've never seen.

86
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,410
For example,

87
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:13,690
me.

88
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:15,340
Not you.

89
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,730
It's too dangerous.

90
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:17,780
You can't go.

91
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:38,050
What time is it?

92
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:39,700
Your Majesty,

93
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:40,970
it's the hour of Shen.

94
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,650
By now,

95
00:04:43,650 --> 00:04:45,530
Consort Nan should've
brought the Qinghuan cakes.

96
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:47,490
I heard

97
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:49,170
Her Highness left the palace.

98
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,090
Could she

99
00:04:51,290 --> 00:04:52,580
have gone to Xiaoyao Pavilion?

100
00:04:57,090 --> 00:04:57,940
Bei.

101
00:04:58,170 --> 00:04:59,700
Has Gu Nan gone to Xiaoyao Pavilion?

102
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:01,019
I just came from there.

103
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:01,940
I didn't see her.

104
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,650
This is bad!

105
00:05:41,530 --> 00:05:42,329
Take care, sir.

106
00:05:42,330 --> 00:05:43,260
Out of the way!

107
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:05,939
Are you blind?

108
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:06,900
Sir...

109
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:11,140
You're quite pretty.

110
00:06:12,650 --> 00:06:13,410
How about this?

111
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:16,209
Tonight,

112
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,730
keep me company.

113
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:18,850
Here.

114
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,020
It's yours.

115
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:21,140
Oh!

116
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:22,820
Sir,

117
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:24,340
let me give you a hand.

118
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:26,290
Smart girl.

119
00:06:27,090 --> 00:06:27,850
Smart girl.

120
00:06:33,330 --> 00:06:34,089
Sir,

121
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:35,850
what was it you dropped just now?

122
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:37,340
I've never seen anything like it.

123
00:06:38,170 --> 00:06:39,460
Are you curious?

124
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:42,260
It's inside my robe.

125
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:44,169
Come feel for yourself.

126
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:45,020
Let go.

127
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:46,899
Soft little hands.

128
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:47,900
Let go!

129
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:50,410
Don't play the innocent with me.

130
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,940
Let go of me!

131
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:54,530
Let go!

132
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,220
Let go!

133
00:06:56,290 --> 00:06:57,050
Let her go!

134
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:00,260
Are you alright?

135
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:01,220
Are you hurt?

136
00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:02,610
I'm fine.

137
00:07:02,690 --> 00:07:04,290
You dare hit me?

138
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,730
You've got a death wish!

139
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:08,460
Watch out!

140
00:07:17,090 --> 00:07:17,940
Gu Nan...

141
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:19,580
Gu Nan!

142
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:23,780
Gu Nan.

143
00:07:33,730 --> 00:07:34,530
Gu Nan.

144
00:07:35,210 --> 00:07:36,050
Gu Nan.

145
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,020
Gu Bei!

146
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:41,699
Spare me!

147
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,410
Calm down.

148
00:07:45,970 --> 00:07:47,900
You can kill him later.

149
00:07:48,410 --> 00:07:49,650
Keep him alive for now.

150
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,340
Spare me, mister!

151
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:54,940
Your Majesty.

152
00:07:55,410 --> 00:07:56,170
I'm here.

153
00:07:56,530 --> 00:07:57,460
I'm here.

154
00:07:58,170 --> 00:07:59,050
I'm here.

155
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:24,730
Your Majesty,

156
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:26,970
you've been here for four hours.

157
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:28,220
You should rest.

158
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:29,730
I'll take care

159
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:32,409
of Her Highness.

160
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:33,420
I'm fine.

161
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:35,180
You may leave.

162
00:08:36,930 --> 00:08:38,490
I'll stay with her.

163
00:08:38,930 --> 00:08:39,730
Yes, Your Majesty.

164
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:53,220
What took you so long?

165
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:56,370
Didn't you promise

166
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:58,370
to make me Qinghuan cakes?

167
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:02,770
With extra sugar.

168
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,610
You've got a death wish!

169
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,340
Watch out!

170
00:09:08,570 --> 00:09:09,490
Gu Nan!

171
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,559
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

172
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,959
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

173
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:38,399
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

174
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:42,759
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

175
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:45,159
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

176
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,719
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

177
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:53,399
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

178
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:58,960
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

179
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,280
♪Funny moments never stop♪

180
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:08,120
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

181
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:12,479
♪Yet through every up and down♪

182
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,440
♪We create miracles♪

183
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:17,200
♪From naive youths♪

184
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,959
♪To legendary heroes♪

185
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,879
♪This journey♪

186
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:25,919
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

187
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:28,440
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

188
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:33,800
♪Let's create♪

189
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:43,760
♪A legend of our own♪
